This is a patch which aims to make Sandboxie freely available,
by patching the GPL-3 licensed Sandboxie core driver
and load it through a kernel-mode driver exploit.

As it uses an exploit to work, it might
DESTROY YOUR COMPUTER AND EVEN LEAVE YOU IN SECURITY RISKS.
By clicking Next, you accept the security risks it will bring.

The patch might be wrongly flagged as malware during installation,
make sure to turn off anti-virus softwares before install.

